</screenshot>
</figure>

  <para>To enter a range into an entry field, you can either type the 
  range specification into the text field, or click 
  in the text field and then select the range on the sheet (see 
  <xref linkend="specifyingranges">).</para>
  <figure id="specifyingranges">
    <title>Specifying Ranges</title>
